00038 template<unsigned DIM>
00039 ExponentialMaterialLaw<DIM>::ExponentialMaterialLaw(double a, double b)
00040     : mA(a),
00041       mB(b)
00042 {
00043     assert(DIM==2 || DIM==3);
00044     if (a < 0.0)
00045     {
00046         EXCEPTION("a must be positive");
00047     }
00048 }

00062 template<unsigned DIM>
00063 double ExponentialMaterialLaw<DIM>::Get_dW_dI1(double I1, double I2)
00064 {
00065     return mA * mB * exp(mB*(I1-DIM));
00066 }
